Package: ananke
Title: Analysis of Time Intervals and Temporal Reasoning
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicolas", "Frerebeau", , "nicolas.frerebeau@u-bordeaux-montaigne.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5759-4944", affiliation = "Université Bordeaux Montaigne"))
Maintainer: Nicolas Frerebeau <nicolas.frerebeau@u-bordeaux-montaigne.fr>
Description: A toolkit for temporal reasoning. This package allows to describe 
    and analyze finite time intervals. It includes tools for radiocarbon 
    calibration and Bayesian chronological modeling.
    It also provides classes and methods for the representation of 
    archaeological sequence diagrams in the framework of Dye and Buck (2015) 
    <doi:10.1016/j.jas.2015.08.008>.
